Mary Grainne O'Brien1

F, #483636, b. January 1905

Last Edited=21 Oct 2012

Mary Grainne O'Brien was born in January 1905.1 She is the daughter of Brian O'Brien and Mary Henrietta Hime.2 She married Ian Galbraith Robson in 1935.1

From 1935, her married name became Robson.
